<paragraph id="8B8B07431601FFEEB59EE154699ACFD2" blockId="23.[160,1155,591,686]" pageId="23" pageNumber="339">This species was found in humid leaf litter under a date palm tree where the soil was rich in accumulations of decayed animal faeces.</paragraph>
